.TH ABRAFLEXI-PREVIEWREPORT 1 "2025-09-20" "abraflexi-report-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-previewreport \- download and preview an invoice using an AbraFlexi report
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-previewreport
.I reportIdent
[\fIinvoiceIdent\fR]
[\fIlanguage\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-previewreport
downloads a PDF generated by AbraFlexi for a selected report and opens it using
.BR xdg-open (1).
The report is selected by its AbraFlexi identifier and can optionally be rendered
for a specific invoice and language.
.PP
If no invoice identifier is supplied, the tool attempts to load the first
available issued invoice and render that document.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I reportIdent
AbraFlexi report identifier, for example
.BR code:TEST3 .
.TP
.I invoiceIdent
Optional AbraFlexi invoice identifier, for example
.BR code:VF1-0001/2023 .
.TP
.I language
Optional output language code, for example
.BR en .
.SH ENVIRONMENT
The tool reads AbraFlexi connection settings from environment variables or a
local
.I .env
file:
.BR ABRAFLEXI_URL ,
.BR ABRAFLEXI_LOGIN ,
.BR ABRAFLEXI_PASSWORD ,
and
.BR ABRAFLEXI_COMPANY .
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Preview a specific invoice with a specific report:
.B abraflexi-previewreport code:TEST3 code:VF1-0001/2023 en
.TP
Preview the first available invoice:
.B abraflexi-previewreport code:TEST3
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-upreport (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Vítězslav Dvořák
